  "tosSection1Para1": "By creating an account, accessing, or using the {appName} mobile application (\"the Service\"), you agree to be bound by these Terma of Service (\"TerTerma If you do not agree to these TTerma you must not access or use the Service.",
  "tosSection1Para2": "The Service is provided by {producer} (\"we\", \"us\", or \"our\"). These Terma form a legally binding agreement between you and us.",
